This repository contains three separately licensed components. Each component
directory carries its full license text; the identifiers below are SPDX.

- apps/inferock-bench — the benchmark CLI and local measurement proxy:
  FSL-1.1-Apache-2.0 (Functional Source License, converting to Apache-2.0).
  See apps/inferock-bench/LICENSE.

- packages/measure — the @inferock/measure library:
  Apache-2.0. See packages/measure/LICENSE.

- spec — the Inferock Standard documents:
  CC-BY-4.0. See spec/LICENSE.

Third-party dependency notices are listed in NOTICE. Vendored third-party
licenses (for example the Xenova claude-tokenizer) are kept alongside the
vendored code.
